{
    "captions":[
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"A mother and her son trek\nacross an endless desert.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:06.758"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Wearing special skin-tight suits\nto dissipate heat and recycle moisture,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:10.428"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"the travelers aren\u2019t worried\nabout dying of thirst.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:14.895"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Their fears are much greater.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:17.693"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"The pair try to walk without rhythm,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:19.924"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"letting the vibrations of their footsteps\nblend into the shifting sands.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:22.259"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"But soon, the sound of the desert\nis drowned out by a louder hissing.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:26.531"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"As a mound of sand races towards them,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:31.174"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"the pair\u2019s unnatural gait\nturns into a sprint.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:33.564"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"The two clamber into a nearby rock face,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:37.274"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"as a sandworm 400 meters long\nbursts from the desert floor.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:39.968"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"This is the world of \"Dune.\"",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:45.090"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Written by Frank Herbert\nand published in 1965,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:48.280"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"\"Dune\" takes place\nin a far-flung future,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:51.803"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"where humanity rules the stars\nin a giant feudal empire.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:54.560"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"This medieval motif goes beyond\njust the government.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:00:58.604"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Unlike most interstellar sci-fi,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:02.149"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Herbert's humans conquered\nthe stars without any computers.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:04.221"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Following an ancient war with robots,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:07.903"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"humanity has forbidden\nthe construction of any machine",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:10.106"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"\u201cin the likeness of a human mind.\u201d",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:13.522"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"But rather than stifling their expansion,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:16.224"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"this edict forced humans\nto evolve in startling ways\u2014",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:18.614"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"becoming biological computers, psychic\nwitches, and prescient space pilots.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:22.414"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Members of these super-powered factions",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:28.065"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"are regularly employed\nby various noble houses,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:30.395"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"all competing for power and new planets\nto add to their kingdoms.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:34.121"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"But almost all these superhuman skills\nrely on the same precious resource:",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:39.081"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"the spice.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:44.332"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"This mystical crop also known as \u201cmelange\u201d\nis essential for all space travel,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:45.792"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"making it the cornerstone\nof the galactic economy.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:51.578"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"And it only grows\non the desert planet Arrakis,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:54.458"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"a dangerous and inhospitable world\nwhose native inhabitants",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:01:57.925"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"have long rebelled against the empire.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:01.546"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Arrakis, also called Dune,\nis the setting for Herbert\u2019s novel,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:04.634"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"which follows Paul\nof the noble House Atreides.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:08.598"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"The book begins with Paul\u2019s family\nbeing assigned control of Dune",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:12.769"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"as part of an elaborate plot\nby their sworn enemies:",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:16.773"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"the sadistic slave drivers\nof House Harkonnen.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:19.939"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"The conflict between these houses upends\nthe delicate political balance on Arrakis.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:23.792"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Soon, Paul is catapulted\ninto the middle of a planetary revolution,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:28.893"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"where he must prove himself capable\nof leading\u2014 and surviving\u2014",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:33.003"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"on this hostile desert world.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:36.946"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"But Arrakis is not simply\nan endless sea of sand.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:39.679"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Herbert was an avid environmentalist,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:43.129"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"who spent over five years creating\nDune\u2019s complex ecosystem.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:45.559"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"The planet is checkered with climate\nbelts and wind tunnels",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:49.507"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"that have shaped its rocky topography.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:52.886"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Different temperate zones produce\nvarying desert flora.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:55.476"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"And almost every element of Dune\u2019s\necosystem works together",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:02:58.344"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"to produce the planet\u2019s essential export.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:01.924"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Herbert\u2019s world building also includes\na rich web of philosophy and religion.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:04.997"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Paul\u2019s mother Jessica, is a member\nof the Bene Gesserit,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:10.526"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"an ancient cult\nof spice-assisted psychics.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:14.046"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Sometimes called \u201cwitches\u201d\nfor their mysterious powers,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:17.181"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"the Bene Gesserit have operated\nas a shadow government for millennia",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:20.140"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"in an effort to guide society\ntowards enlightenment.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:24.293"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Similarly ancient are the Mentats\u2014",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:28.121"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"human computers capable\nof processing incredible amounts of data.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:30.601"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"While the Mentats are bastions\nof logic and reason,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:34.778"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"their results are not mere calculations,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:37.549"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"but rather, streams of constantly\nshifting possibilities.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:40.003"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"However, no group is more central\nto \"Dune\" than the Fremen.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:44.070"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Natives of Arrakis, they are the keepers\nof the planet\u2019s many secrets.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:48.431"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Paul\u2019s journey takes him deep\ninto the Fremen\u2019s exclusive brotherhood,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:53.255"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"where he must prove himself trustworthy",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:56.785"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"in a series of increasingly\ndeadly challenges.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:03:58.784"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"All these factions have deep histories\nthat pervade the text,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:02.036"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"and Herbert also incorporates that\nsense of scale into the book\u2019s structure.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:05.417"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Each chapter begins with a quote\nfrom a future history book,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:09.886"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"recalling elements of the events\nthat are about to unfold.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:13.286"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"The book also contains in-universe\nappendices",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:16.776"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"that further explore the Empire\u2019s history;",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:20.067"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"alongside a glossary of words like\n\u201cGom jabbar\u201d and \u201cShai-Hulud.\"",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:22.636"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"Dune\u2019s epic story continues to unfold\nover a six-book saga that spans millennia.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:27.475"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"But every story of Arrakis\u2019\nfuture begins here:",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:33.515"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"as Paul pursues a path\nthat is dangerous, demanding,",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:36.945"
       },
       {
          "duration":0,
          "content":"and always on the verge of being\nconsumed by the oncoming storm.",
          "startOfParagraph":null,
          "startTime":"00:04:41.110"
       }
    ]
 }